lead_paragraph: Aerial Powers scored a season-high 30 points with nine rebounds and No. 18 Michigan State rolled past Wisconsin 77-54 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Powers Leads No. 18 Michigan St. Women Over Wisconsin 77-54
